731
00:27:42,680 --> 00:27:43,520
No problem.

732
00:27:43,640 --> 00:27:45,070
You can give him some hints.

733
00:27:45,070 --> 00:27:46,940
Don't let him lose too badly.

734
00:27:47,360 --> 00:27:48,200
No need.

735
00:27:48,400 --> 00:27:49,300
I can do it alone.

